## 18. System Flow Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["Start Program"] --> B["Open Webcam & Initialize MediaPipe"]
    B --> C["Begin Calibration (5 seconds)"]
    C --> D{"Face Detected?"}
    D -- No --> E["Show 'No Face' warning"] --> C
    D -- Yes --> F["Collect EAR samples"]
    F --> G{"5 seconds elapsed?"}
    G -- No --> C
    G -- Yes --> H["Compute baseline EAR\nthreshold = max(baseline × 0.75, 0.12)"]
    H --> I["=== MAIN MONITORING LOOP ==="]
    
    I --> J["Capture Frame → Detect Face"]
    J --> K{"Face Found?"}
    K -- No --> L["Status = NO FACE"] --> V
    K -- Yes --> M["Calculate EAR & MAR"]
    
    M --> N["Update PERCLOS (30s rolling window)"]
    N --> O["Count Blinks (closed→open edges)"]
    O --> P{"EYE_COUNTER ≥ 20?"}
    P -- Yes --> Q["Status = DROWSY\nRed flash + Beep alert"]
    P -- No --> R{"PERCLOS ≥ 25%?"}
    R -- Yes --> S["Status = FATIGUED"]
    R -- No --> T{"MAR > 0.5?"}
    T -- Yes --> U["Status = YAWNING\n(count yawns, burst alert every 3)"]
    T -- No --> V["Status = AWAKE"]
    
    Q & S & U & V --> W["Draw HUD Panel + Face Contours"]
    W --> X["Display Frame"]
    X --> Y{"'q' pressed?"}
    Y -- No --> J
    Y -- Yes --> Z["Release Camera & Exit"]
```

