## Quick Reference — Key Variables

| Variable | Type | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `EAR_THRESHOLD` | `float` | Dynamically set during calibration. EAR below this = eyes "closed" |
| `MAR_THRESHOLD` | `float` | Fixed at 0.5. MAR above this = mouth open (yawning) |
| `EYE_COUNTER` | `int` | Leaky integrator: +1 when closed, −1 when open. Hits 20 = DROWSY |
| `perclos_deque` | `deque` | Rolling 30s buffer of (timestamp, is_closed) tuples |
| `perclos_val` | `float` | Current PERCLOS ratio (0.0–1.0). ≥0.25 = FATIGUED |
| `total_blinks` | `int` | Counts closed→open transitions |
| `YAWN_COUNT` | `int` | Total yawns detected this session |
| `YAWN_COOLDOWN` | `bool` | Prevents counting the same yawn event twice |
